text: Landasan hukum yang digunain, tuh, ada Peraturan Menteri Kominfo No. 5 Tahun 2020 tentang Penyelenggara Sistem Elektronik (PSE) Lingkup Privat, Peraturan Pemerintah No. 71 Tahun 2019, dan Peraturan Menteri Kominfo No. 10 Tahun 2021.
en_text: The legal basis used, there is a Minister of Communication and Information Regulation No. 5 of 2020 concerning the Organizer of the Electronic System (PSE) Private Scope, Government Regulation No. 71 of 2019, and Minister of Communication and Information Regulation No. 10 of 2021.
